	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-09-21T10:38:27">Sepura plc (Sepura) is a United Kingdom-based company engaged in the design, development and supply of digital radio solutions, complementary accessories, support tools and devices. The Company's products include TErrestrial Trunked RAdio (TETRA), Digital Mobile Radio (DMR) and Multi-Platform. TETRA is an open digital trunked mobile radio standard developed to meet the needs of Professional Mobile Radio (PMR) user organizations, including public safety, transportation, utilities, government, military, commercial and industry, and oil and gas. DMR is an open digital standard that defines a direct digital replacement for analogue PMR. DMR serves a range of users from trunked mission-critical applications through to single buildings. Its Multi-Platform product applications include image messaging, message and query. Its subsidiaries include Sepura Systems GmbH, Sepura Deutschland GmbH, Sepura LLC, Sepura Mexico, S.A. de C.V., Fylde Micro Limited and Portalify OY.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2015-11-26T09:47:40">BRIEF: For the six months ended 02 October 2015, Sepura Plc revenues increased 70% to EUR92.9M. Net loss totaled EUR6.1M vs. income of EUR3.8M. Revenues reflect an increase in demand for the Company's products and services due to favorable market conditions. Net loss reflects Administrative Expenses increase of 92% to EUR11.1M (expense), Non-Recurring Costs increase from EUR642K to EUR5.4M (expense).</Text>
	</TextInfo>
